# T2 OpenClaude Context — loads on: openclaude, whatsapp, voice, tts, mcp-server, openclaw

## OpenClaude Architecture
- Stack: Claude Code + MCP servers + Edge TTS + WhatsApp bridge
- Queue: keyed (one slot per sender); newer overwrites pending
- Timeouts: 30s tool-call (hard) | 90s total (soft) → fallback text reply
- Crash recovery: supervisor, 5s backoff, max 3 restarts/hour
- Rule: WhatsApp log-only; NEVER reply without explicit owner authorization

